sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant Backend as Node.js Backend<br/>(Fastify) 8080/TCP
    participant GenAI as gen-ai BFF<br/>8143/TCP TLS
    participant MaaS as MaaS BFF<br/>8243/TCP TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LlamaStack as LlamaStack Server<br/>HTTPS
    participant MaaSAPI as MaaS API Server<br/>HTTPS

    Note over Browser, K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Request to Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)<br/>TLS
    Note right of KRBP: Validates user can<br/>list OpenShift projects
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User<br/>X-Auth-Request-Groups
    Backend-->>KRBP: HTML/JS/CSS (React SPA)
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: Dashboard UI

    Note over Browser, K8sAPI: Flow 1b: API Request (K8s pass-through)

    Browser->>Gateway: GET /api/k8s/... (HTTPS/443)<br/>Authorization: Bearer {token}
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: K8s API Request (HTTPS/6443)<br/>Impersonation: user identity<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: K8s Response
    Backend-->>KRBP: JSON Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: JSON Response

    Note over Browser, LlamaStack: Flow 2: Module Federation BFF Request (gen-ai example)

    Browser->>Gateway: POST /gen-ai/api/v1/llama/responses<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward (HTTPS/8443)
    KRBP->>Backend: Forward (HTTP/8080)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>GenAI: Proxy (HTTPS/8143)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token<br/>TLS
    Note right of GenAI: RequireAccessToService<br/>validates token via K8s API
    GenAI->>LlamaStack: POST /inference/chat_completion<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token<br/>TLS 1.2+
    LlamaStack-->>GenAI: LLM Response
    GenAI-->>Backend: JSON Response
    Backend-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: Chatbot Response

    Note over Browser, MaaSAPI: Flow 3: WebSocket K8s Watch

    Browser->>Gateway: WS Upgrade /wss/k8s/...<br/>WSS/443 TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: WSS/8443 TLS
    KRBP->>Backend: WS/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Backend->>K8sAPI: WSS/6443<br/>Bearer Token (subprotocol)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Backend: Watch Events (stream)
    Backend-->>KRBP: WS Frames
    KRBP-->>Gateway: WSS Frames
    Gateway-->>Browser: Real-time Updates

    Note over GenAI, MaaSAPI: Flow 4: Inter-BFF Communication

    GenAI->>MaaS: POST /maas/api/v1/tokens<br/>HTTPS/8243 TLS 1.2+<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    MaaS->>MaaSAPI: Token Request<br/>HTTPS, Bearer Token
    MaaSAPI-->>MaaS: Token Response
    MaaS-->>GenAI: Token Data
